  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The &quot;Chinese PAC&quot; study (CLDT600ACN03) will evaluate the efficacy and safety of open label
      telbivudine in 2,200 compensated Chronic Hepatitis B (CHB) adults. The primary objective of
      the study is the proportion of patients achieving undetectable HBV DNA at week 52.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
